FBIS3-51107 "drlat009_m_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-009 Document Type:Daily Report 13 Jan 1994 Brazil Deputy Luiz Santos Named Government Leader in Chamber PY1301005194 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television in Portuguese 2200 GMT 12 Jan 94 PY1301005194 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] The government has a new leader in the Chamber of Deputies. He is Deputy Luiz Carlos Santos of the PMDB [Brazilian Democratic Movement Party] of Sao Paulo. He replaces Deputy Roberto Freire.
